options.content:
# README 

JupyterHub exposes certain metrics in a way that prometheus can understand. More information
on the metrics exposed by JupyterHub can be found at [JupyterHub](https://jupyterhub.readthedocs.io/en/stable/reference/metrics.html) 
official documentation.

-  All average metrics presented in the stats are average in the range selected in Grafana main dashboard
- Nb running servers and Nb active users are current number of running servers and logged in hub users
- Average server spawn and proxy metrics are the average time taken in the range selected.
